      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.html",
      "filePath": "admin/index.html",
      "summary": "Main admin dashboard shell with Supabase email login, tabbed panels for gold price CRUD and product catalog management (products, brands, categories), inline gold table editing with audit history and Excel export, and a password-change modal wired to client-side admin modules.",
      "tags": ["admin", "dashboard", "crud", "gold-pricing", "catalog"],
